Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Other House
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While I was hanging up the laundry,\Nthe phone rang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I picked up the receiver,\Na thin voice said, "Hello?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He continued, "Is now a good time?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought this might be that "Hey, it's me" scam\NI heard on the news, so I raised my guard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then the voice said,\N"It's been a while. It's Rei."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The owner of the voice was a boy who had lived\Nin my home up until a few years earlier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Tarou.\NHow have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tarou's become an old man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lately all he does is sleep there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right, Tarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is Ayumu doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Kyouko, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumu is going to a prep school,\Nand I guess you'd say Kyouko is a temp worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She works here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I answered him, I was relieved\Nthat he came to visit when I was alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Kyouko and Ayumu were here, this living room\Nwould have become cold in an instant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like it did back then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, these are sweets from a shop run by\Na family that's been helping me a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. These days, in this house,\Nno one speaks his name anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for not being able\Nto visit in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I was worried about you\Nsince you never came by."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was going to say that, but stopped myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This boy understood everything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and did us a favor by staying away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I awkwardly sat with him,\Nunable to look him in the eyes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he still sat across from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So mellow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it, mellow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He seems much more mellow now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He'd become an adult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he the same age as Ayumu?\NI can't believe it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My son hasn't even changed,\Nand he's still a child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I realized my children were no match for him\Nat a fairly early stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a simple situation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyone could see that the amount\Nof practice he did was unbelievable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:03:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if they didn't want to lose to him, they would\Nhave to practice even more than he did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a simple answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, could they do it? No, they couldn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He silently embodied sound reasoning\Nand in his presence,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my children's own weakness\Nmade them lose their equilibrium{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and they collapsed into pieces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When my own children\Nturned against me, I was lost,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and my husband silently watched it all unfold.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"People who need other people to motivate them\Nwill eventually come up against a brick wall."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was his view.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unable to look at their weak selves,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they became caught up in enjoyments\Nwithin their reach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day, Ayumu declared,\N"Being able to make an effort is a talent too!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To those words,\Nmy husband just chuckled, "Haha."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:04:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think that was the moment he gave up\Non Ayumu becoming a professional shogi player.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being around that boy, they realized that\Npeople who wanted to reach a certain place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}had to pursue it to that extent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I always thought "only a small handful\Nof people can become what they want to be."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I never thought about\Nwhat you have to do to become something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so that boy's situation\Nwas a dreary weight on my chest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then one day,\NI finally came to a realization.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That my husband\Nhad a similar childhood as that boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I understood, but I really didn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looking past shogi,\Nout of all the people in the house,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the person my husband related to the most\Nwasn't a family member, but that boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was wholeheartedly dedicated to shogi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}silently studied and did homework,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and even helped out around the house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He really was a good boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that made my children suffer all the more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is he such a good boy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why didn't my children turn out like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What were the differences between the way his\Nmother raised him and how I raised my kids?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I fail in raising my children?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or is he just playing the role of a "good boy"\Nas best he can since he's a freeloader?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe he's laughing at us behind our backs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei really was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just a really good boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:06:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My children understood that, and so did I.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We took advantage of him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We took advantage, pushed him away,\Ntreated him shoddily,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and didn't give him a place to belong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so he felt like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The longer I'm around, the more strained\Neveryone's relations will become."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he didn't even say that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He just quietly left the house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the five o'clock bell rang out,\NRei got up from his chair.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He said, "Well..." and skipped\Nany other closing remarks,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}apart from, "I'll come again."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Yes, come again," I answered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, what else could I say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Live a long life, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After Rei left, I started preparing dinner\Nin the kitchen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As always.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if no one calls me, I stand here every day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I make dinner and wait for everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That night, I had a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the dream, Rei was really my son.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that he was my son,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei was sprawled out in the living room,\Neating junk food, watching TV,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when I told him to go to bed,\Nhe retorted, "Oh, be quiet!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought to myself,\N"Well! He's the same as Ayumu and Kyouko."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was disappointed and yet also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}profoundly relieved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Other House
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Child of March Town
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Let's go to a monjayaki place."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kiriyama invited us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}before Takahashi left for Kouchi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MONJA JIROU
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um, both of you,\Ncongratulations on your graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I wish you the best of luck\Nat the private school in Kouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, cheer—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, congratulations\Non your promotion to B-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C-Congratulations, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:41.72,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUST FOUND OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:43.10,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ADMIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My grandpa was so psyched about\Npersonally knowing a B class shogi player.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Yes! My teacher made it to B class!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was so proud\Nthat he couldn't contain himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Kiriyama is a future Meijin!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for losing so quickly\Nat that last NHK Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And they were really looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, naw, Grandpa was like,\N"Next up is the Lion King Championship!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's already excited about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salmon monja and mentai mochi with cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Thanks.\N- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, you're totally my grandpa's idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before he would mostly be in bed, but recently\Nhe popped in at the neighborhood shogi club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}SHOGI CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are happy too\Nthat he's back on his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're like, "Professionals are incredible!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I want to become a professional soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}"I want to become a professional."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Not "someday." He said "soon."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you sure?\N- Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:12:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In Takahashi's mind, becoming a professional\Nhas gone from a "dream" to a "goal."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MONJA JIROU
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A person who helped me back in little league\Nis now the coach of the school in Kouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All the best players are concentrated in Tokyo,\Nand there are a lot of infielders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, there are dozens of schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to raise my chances of getting\Nto the high school nationals, even by a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided to go where that coach is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With Takahashi's practiced hands\Nand the clanging of the spatula,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the familiar sizzling sound\Nand delicious scent rose up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:13:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this spring,\NTakahashi will be leaving March Town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they have monja in Kouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they don't, I can make it.\NAll I need is a hot plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can get the ingredients\Nat any supermarket, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll be bringing some sliced squid, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they're having\Na welcome party at the dorm,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd make this as a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like saying, "I'm from March Town."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're children of March Town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter where we go,\Nthat will never change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they know what "monja" is,\Nthey probably haven't tried it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. And I'm sure it'll be good\Nif Takahashi makes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Grandpa told me\Nto at least take some spatulas for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The bamboo kind to use with hot plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. They probably don't sell this\Nlittle kind there. Even if they have big ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It suddenly felt like I was going to cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was really going to leave this place soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I caught myself on the verge of tears\Na number of times, but I held my breath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next week Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the day of the Cherry Blossom Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's too bad I have to miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you do another food stand, Kawamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This time we're making\Nsweet red bean soup. Two kinds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cool. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time is precious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's flowing onward and I can't stop it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so happy that Rei invited me, giving me\Nthe chance to talk to Takahashi a lot at the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's great that we got to have monja together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was great.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, the morning of\Nthe Cherry Blossom Festival came.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.69,LeftSignL2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.69,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SWEET RED BEAN SOUP\NAZUKI\NWALNUT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}TEA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, preparations complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who would like some\Nsweet red bean soup with rice dumplings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Crescent Moon is serving up\Ntasty food again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's thick, sweet, and salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good to hear! It has light-brown miso inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This warms me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's still chilly by the riverside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then I'll have\Nsome sweet red bean soup with walnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HEAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Tupperware containing\Nthe cash made from sales
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, business is booming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's still cold outside, so going with\Nsomething warm was the right choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you start running low\Non dumplings, let me know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:38.20,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MERCHANT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll boil up as many as we need!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, you call out the secret phrase,\N"Brown sugar syrup roasted soy flour!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Got it!\N- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't want to see him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MILK TAKAHASHI
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good luck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Takahashi. I'm going to do my best here, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Two soups with walnuts, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hina cut her hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a major event in a young girl's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Did she cut her hair\Nbecause a crush was quashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! She suddenly told me last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so bittersweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, I'm thinking of getting a haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? S-Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this that legendary...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will cut my hair{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to give a proper send-off to my childhood self{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and to take a step forward as the new me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell she was reading\Nthat kind of poem in her head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can I put it? I'm at a loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My little sister is too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the springtime of her life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina! It's so bittersweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari, don't you dare\Nsay any of that to Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}UMM...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she would faint\Nout of embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina! How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the beauty salon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GLOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:23.12,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EHH!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a failure.\NI'm never leaving the house again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to high school\Nfrom the second semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here, let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very middle school look...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:49.39,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHIVER\NSHIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean such a high school look...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}TINY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, a-anyway,\Nit looks really good on you! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:20:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I asked her to give me an adult-like bob...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But only an old woman was at the salon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hina! A bob?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oof...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hina? I thought it was a household deity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}HA-WHA?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:22.51,OnTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YOU CAN'T\NSAY THAT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kokeshi doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, how could you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}NOOO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Apparently trying\Nto cheer her up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hina, here! Hina!\N- I'm never going outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a shut-in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it in any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Hina!\NHold this just for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CANDY DROPS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You too, Sis?!\N- Come on, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Please, just for a little bit!\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Oh please, Hina?\N- Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Child of March Town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, Kiriyama has come to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! If you don't come out,\NKiriyama is going to be late, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, just resign yourself to it and come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:07.51,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STARE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's weird, isn't it?\NI-I never should've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks stupid, doesn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}HAWAWA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really do look like that household deity\Nwith the bowl hairstyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:18.19,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WAHHH
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.40,0:23:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Huh?
